Comment: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:06.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ジパング国ナンバー1の武芸者を目指すムサシは、あまたの武芸者と剣を交えたのであったが、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:06.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지팡구국 제일의 무예가를 꿈꾸는 무사시는 무수한 무예가와 검을 주고받고 있었지만
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:06.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dreaming for the number one martial artist of Jipangu State, Musashi was fighting against numberless Martial Artists,
Comment: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:14.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,出会った相手が悪かった。今や全国に多くの会員を持つ悪名高いヨシオカ道場のボス、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:14.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,상대를 잘못 만났다. 지금은 전국에서 많은 회원을 가진 악명 높은 요시오카 도장의 보스,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:14.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,but he met a wrong opponent, the infamous Denshichirō, the boss of Yoshika Dōjō
Comment: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,デンシチローを敵に回してしまったのであった。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,덴시치로를 적으로 맞이하고야 말았다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,boasting countless members across the land.
Comment: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,ja,0,0,60,,名刀コタツ、嵐を呼ぶだス
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,ko,0,0,60,,명검 코테츠, 폭풍을 부르오
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,en,0,0,200,,Kotetsu the Excellent Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,en,0,0,60,,Calls for a Storm
Comment: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:40.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そのような{???}で勝負を挑むなど笑止千万！武芸者の勝負とは、このような真剣を使って{???}ものよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:40.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 목검으로 승부를 보다니 가소롭기 짝이 없구나! 무예가의 승부라는 것은 이런 진검을 써서 하는 것이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:35.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's very absurd, to have a match with that wooden sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:40.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,A match between martial artists shall only be done with real swords like this!
Comment: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やられた！おいら死んじまうだス！誰か助けてくれだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당했소! 나, 죽겠소! 누가 살려주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,I lost! I'm going to die-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Someone help me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:00.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,坊や、何を寝ぼけているんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:00.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,얘야. 뭘 자면서 그러니.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:00.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kid, you're half asleep.
Comment: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これは柿でござるだスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이건 감이었소...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,It was a persimmon-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:10.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さき、柿の木の下をとった時におこってきたんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:10.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아까 감나무 아래 지나가는 중에 떨어졌나 보구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:10.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,We were going under a persimmon tree moments ago.
Comment: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何夢を見ていたか知らんが、{???}興奮さしてたぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 꿈을 꾸고 있었는지는 모르겠지만 크게 흥분하고 있었구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't know what were you dreaming about, but you were pretty agitated.
Comment: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,畜生、おいらも刀が欲しいんだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 나도 칼을 원하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn, I want a sword too-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:25.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,刀を手に入れてジパングナンバー1の武芸者になってやるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:25.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼을 손에 넣어 지팡구 제일의 무예가가 되겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:25.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will get a sword and become the number one martial artist of Jipangu-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ほれ、もうすぐサカイの街だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어이! 이제 곧 사카이 마을이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,We're soon at Sakai village.
