Comment: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:52.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これがわがヨシオカ道場に狼藉を働いたムサシの顔だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:52.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 자가 우리 요시오카 도장에 행패를 부린 무사시의 얼굴이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:52.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is the face of Musashi who wreaked havoc on our Yoshioka Dōjō.
Comment: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんで狂暴なかが！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,매우 교활한 얼굴이군!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a sly face!
