Comment: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:59.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,奴ら、間違いなくこのサカイの町にいるはずだ。いいか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:59.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,녀석은 틀림없이 이 사카이 마을에 있을 터이다. 알겠나?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:59.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,He should be in this Sakai village. Understood?
Comment: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:05.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,草の根を分けても奴を探し出し、見つけたら直ちにこの俺に知らせろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:05.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,샅샅이 뒤져서라도 녀석을 찾아내어 발견하면 바로 이 나에게 알려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:05.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Search for him thoroughly and report to me as soon as you find out where he is!
Comment: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ガキだと思って油断すると痛い目にあうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,애송이라 생각될 테지만 방심하면 큰일난다!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,He is not just a weak brat, so be careful!
Comment: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,は！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Comment: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:13.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:13.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:13.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master!
