Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:14.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,例の刀鍛冶が参りました。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예의 칼 장인이 오셨습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,The sword craftsman you asked for is here.
Comment: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よし。今行く。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋다. 지금 가겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good. I'll go right now.
Comment: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:32.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,この人物、剣持コテツこそ、ジパング国の長い戦国時代の歴史上有名な刀鍛冶である。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:32.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 인물, 켄모치 코테츠야말로, 지팡구국의 기나긴 전국 시대의 역사적으로 유명한 칼 장인이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:32.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,This person, Kenmochi Kotetsu, is a historically famous sword craftsman of the long Sengoku period of Jipangu State.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.42,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz26\fs32\fad(0,300)\pos(337,242)\c&H8989FF&}코테츠 작
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.42,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz26\fs32\fad(0,300)\pos(337,242)\c&H8989FF&}Made by Kotetsu
Comment: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:40.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,彼の作った刀は、コテツと呼ばれ、剣の道を究めたものだけが手にすることができたと言われる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:40.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그가 만든 칼은 코테츠라 불리며, 검의 길을 끝까지 걸은 자만이 손에 넣을 수 있다고 불려진다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:40.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,A sword crafted by him is called Kotetsu, and it is told that only masters of swords can have one.
Comment: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:51.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,拙者、ヨシオカ道場を師範代、ヨシオカデンシチローと申す。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:51.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나는 요시오카 도장의 대리 사범, 요시오카 덴시치로라고 하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:51.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Denshichirō Yoshioka, a substitute instructor at Yoshioka Dōjō.
Comment: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,剣持コテツです。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,켄모치 코테츠이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kenmochi Kotetsu.
Comment: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,早速だが、拙者に名刀コテツを作ってもらいたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,본론부터 말하자면, 내게 명도 코테츠를 만들어 주셨으면 한다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Long story short, I'd like to ask you to make your excellent sword Kotetsu.
Comment: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お断りする。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거절하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,I reject.
Comment: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何？このヨシオカ道場師範代の頼みをお断るだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐라?! 이 요시오카 도장의 대리 사범의 요청을 거절한다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! You dare to reject the request from the substitute instructor at Yoshioka Dōjō?
Comment: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:14.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おぬし、まさか、ジパング国に名高いヨシオカデンシチロー様を知らないのではなかろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:14.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너, 설마 지팡구국에 이름을 떨치는 요시오카 덴시치로 님을 모르는 것인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:14.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't you know Yoshioka Denshichirō, a name famous all over Jipangu State?
Comment: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,存じておる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이름은 안다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,I do know.
Comment: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:22.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ならどうして断る。刀を作るものとして、これほど面妖なことはないではないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:22.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 어째서 거절하나? 칼을 만드는 게 그렇게 체면 구기는 일은 아니지 않소이까.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:22.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then why do you reject? Crafting a sword isn't something dishonorable.
Comment: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,残念だが、もはや刀鍛冶は汎用いたした。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안됐지만 이미 칼 만드는 것은 그만두었소.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,I regret to say that I already gave up crafting swords.
Comment: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やめた？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,관두었다?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Gave up?
Comment: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どうだ。金ならいくらでも出すぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떤가. 돈이라면 얼마라도 주겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,How's this? We'll pay as much as you want.
Comment: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わしは金など欲しくはない。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 돈 따위를 원하는 것이 아니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,I do not want money.
Comment: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.53,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ならば何が望みだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다면 무엇을 바라는가?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then what do you want?
Comment: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何も。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아무것도.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Comment: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,欲のない奴だ。だがよく覚えておけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,욕심 없는 녀석이군. 그러나 잘 기억해 두어라.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see that you are without greed. But know this.
Comment: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:46.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おぬしにどのような事情があれ、この俺に刀を一振り作ってもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:46.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네게 어떤 사정이 있던간, 이 내게 칼을 하나 만들어 바쳐야 할 것이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:46.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Whatever reason you have, you will make and give me a sword.
Comment: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,失礼いたす。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,실례하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待て！まだ話は終わっておらん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠깐! 아직 이야기가 끝나지 않았다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait! He is not done yet!
Comment: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,期限は十日間！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기한은 10일간!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will allow you ten days!
Comment: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,この俺が直々に取りに行く。分かったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 내가 직접 가지러 가겠다. 알겠나?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will go receive it myself. Understood?
Comment: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,大丈夫でしょうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,괜찮습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you alright with this?
Comment: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,子のジパング広いと言えどもいまだかって俺の頼みを断ったものはおらぬわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 지팡구가 넓을 망정 일찍이 내 부탁을 거절한 자는 없었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,No matter how wide Jipangu is, nobody dared to deny my request.
Comment: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:13.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もっとも、断ったばかりに命を失ったものは数知れぬがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:13.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,더욱, 거절한 것으로 생명을 잃은 자는 수를 셀 수가 없군.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:13.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Moreover, I can't count how many people lost their lives by denying my request.
Comment: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、腹が減って死にそうでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나... 배고파 죽겠소...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am starved to death-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こ、これはお団子のにおいでござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이, 이건 단고의 향이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,This smell must be dango-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
