Comment: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わー！天の助けでござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우와! 하늘의 도움이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wow! It's a help from the heavens-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,みんな！乗ってるかい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모두! 타셨습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you ready?!
Comment: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,イェーイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes!
Comment: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:08.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よし、早速働いてもらおうか。なに、仕事は簡単。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:08.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋아, 바로 일해 볼까? 일은 간단해.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:08.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get you working right away. Your job is simple.
Comment: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,注文が来たら運び行くだけでいいんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주문이 들어오면 가져다 주기만 하면 돼.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bring these whenever there is an order.
Comment: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,って、食事はなんじでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저, 식사는 몇시이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,When is the mealtime-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,働いてから食事だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,일하고 나서 식사다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,After you work.
Comment: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,3番テーブル団子いっちょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,3번 테이블 단고 한 접시!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,One dango plate on the 3th table!
Comment: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はいよ！団子いっちょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네! 단고 한 접시!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it! One dango plate!
Comment: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ほらほら、早くもって行って！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어이, 어이, 빨리 가져다 줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Hurry up and bring it!
Comment: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え、はい、はい、はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네, 네, 네!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Comment: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、ここだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 이곳이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here it is-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お待ちどうだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리셨소!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here is your order-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ほれ、オツルちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라? 오츠루 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? Otsuru!
Comment: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え、なによ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐에요?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:39.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やっぱりオツルさんだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:39.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 오츠루 씨인 것이오! 나이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:39.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're Otsuru-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! It's me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:41.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,私、あんたなんか知らないわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:41.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,전 당신이 누군지 몰라요.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:41.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are.
Comment: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:46.20,Default,ja,0,0,0,,また冗談言って。おいらだスよ！ミヤモト村のムサシだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:46.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에이, 장난은 관두고 나이오, 나! 미야모토 마을의 무사시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:46.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't joke on me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I am Musashi, from Miyamoto village-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシなんて知らないわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시라니 몰라요!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't know anyone named Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi?
Comment: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.78,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オツルちゃん、おいらだスよ、やだな！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨, 나에요, 나!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru, it's me!
Comment: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.50,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何言ってんのよ！あたいの名前はオタマっていうのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 소리에요! 내 이름은 오타마에요!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?! My name is Otama!
Comment: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オツルちゃんったら怒った顔もなかなかかわいいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨도 참 화나면 귀엽소...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru, you're cute when you're angry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:06.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なにすんのよ！誰か！痴漢よ、この人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:06.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 짓이야! 아무나! 이 사람 치한이에요!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:06.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Help me! A pervert!
Comment: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ち、違うだス。違うだスよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아니오! 아니오!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, that's not it! There's a misunderstanding-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:16.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え、困るんだよね。そうでなくても最近PTAがうるさいんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:16.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이러면 곤란해. 그러지 않아도 최근 학부모회가 시끄럽게 구는데.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:16.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was pretty bad. We don't need to trigger PTA any further...
Comment: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ごめんだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,죄송하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm sorry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:23.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,まあ、君には{???}ほうんの仕事は向いていないみたいだから、え、そこで団子の櫛でも削ってもらおうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:23.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네게 식당 앞 일은 어울리지 않는 것 같으니 저기서 단고 막대기라도 깎아라.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:23.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,It seems that you're not suited for working at the front of house. Maybe you're better off with carving dango sticks.
Comment: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あの、食事は。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저, 식사는...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Uh, the meal...
Comment: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,-まだまだ！\N-え、はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-아직아직!\N-네...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Not yet!\N-Okay...
Comment: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お茶屋でムサシが働いています。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 찻집 안에서 무사시가 일하고 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is working in this tea house.
Comment: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:42.13,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシめ、今日という今日は決着を付けてやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:42.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 놈, 오늘로써 끝장을 내 주겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:42.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, you're going down as of today!
Comment: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いいか？絶対武蔵を逃すではないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠나? 절대 무사시를 놓치면 안 된다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Understand? Do not let Musashi run away!
Comment: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Roger!
Comment: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:53.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ほお、人には何か一つ取柄があるというが。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:53.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오? 네게도 하나 잘 하는 것이 있구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:53.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh , at least you have a specialty.
Comment: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシはどこだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 어디 있나!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where is Musashi?!
Comment: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あの声は。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 저 목소리는...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,That voice...
Comment: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,な、何をするんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐냐, 뭔 짓이냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Comment: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えい、どけ！ムサシがいたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,비켜라! 무사시가 있다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Move away! Musashi is here!
Comment: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ！覚悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Prepare yourself!
Comment: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシはこっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 저깄다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,There's Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待ってやがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈춰라!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop!
Comment: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵が屋根の上を逃げていくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시가 저 지붕에서 달아난다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is running away on that roof!
Comment: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,くっそ、しつこいでござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 끈덕지오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,They're damn persistent-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:09:59.38,0:09:59.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:09:59.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:09:59.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ！覚悟するんだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 각오해라.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Prepare yourself.
Comment: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:21.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,畜生！さあ、やれるもんならやってみるだス。たった一人大勢なんて卑怯だス！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:21.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장! 자, 하려면 하시오! 겨우 하나 대 여럿이라니 비겁하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:21.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dammit! Do as you want-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! One vs many is cowardly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:26.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,卑怯とは言わせん。お前なんぞ俺一人で十分わ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:26.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,비겁이라고 말하면 안 된다. 너 따위는 나 혼자서도 충분하다!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:26.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not call this cowardly. I am more than enough to finish you!
Comment: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オツルちゃん！さっきにあの世に行ってるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}오츠루 씨! 먼저 다음 세계로 가겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otsuru! I'm going to the next world earlier than you-{\i0}dasu{\i1}!
Comment: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシめ！追え！追うんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 놈! 쫒아라! 쫒아!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn that Musashi! Follow him! Find him!
Comment: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どうしたでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 일이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's going on-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあ！今のうちだ！来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자! 이 틈이다! 따라와!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now! Run away! Come!
Comment: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,,助かったでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살았소...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a relief-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,礼を言う。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,감사하...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,I must say thank...
Comment: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コ、コジロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:00.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,礼儀じらずめ。いの著の恩人を呼び捨てにする奴があるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:00.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예의 모르는 놈. 생명의 은인 이름을 막 부르는 놈이 있는가!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:00.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,You insolent brat. How rude of you to call the name of your lifesaver without respect!
Comment: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ごめんだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미안하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sorry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ありがとうでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,고맙소.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,って、でもなんでおいらを助けたんだスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 근데 왜 날 구했소?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bu- but why did you saved me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:14.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お前のようなガキ一匹を大の大人が寄ってたかって追い回すようなヨシオカのやり方は許せんからだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:14.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너같은 꼬맹이 하나를 다 자란 성인 여럿이서 쫒아다니는 요시오카의 짓은 용서할 수 없기 때문이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:14.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive how the numerous grown-ups at Yoshioka are trying to chase a young kid like you!
Comment: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらはガキではないだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 얘가 아니오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am not a kid!
Comment: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,じゃ、お前はなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 넌 뭐냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then what are you?
Comment: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、こう見えても武芸者だス。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 이렇게 보여도 무예가라오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am a martial artist despite how I look-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:26.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん、笑わせるな。自分の刀も持ってんガキが！恥知らずめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:26.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥, 웃기지 마라! 자기 칼도 없는 얘가! 부끄러운 줄 모르는 놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:26.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph, don't make me laugh! You don't even have your own sword! You should be ashamed!
Comment: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そ、それは言い過ぎだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 그건 너무했소!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Th- that's too much!
Comment: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,剣は武士の命！剣の持たぬ奴を武士とは認めん！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,검은 무사의 생명! 검을 가지지 않는 놈을 무사로는 인정할 수 없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,A sword is the life of a martial artist! I will not accept whoever without a sword as a martial artist!
Comment: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:41.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,,この件は名刀関の孫六、通称物干し竿だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:41.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 칼은 명도 세키노마고로쿠(関の孫六). 통칭 모노호시자오(物干し竿)다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:41.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,This excellent sword is Seki no Magoroku, also known as Monohoshizao.
Comment: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よく拝んでおけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 봐 두어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Feast your eyes!
Comment: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん。ばっかめ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥. 바보 놈.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph. Idiot.
Comment: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.97,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐시라?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,What did you say-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,かっこつけるんじゃないでござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멋진 척 하지 마시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're a showoff-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,助かったでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살았소...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was close-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジローのやつめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로 놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn that Kojirō!
Comment: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:20.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジローに馬鹿にされたムサシ。刀を手根入れることができるのか。疾風怒濤の後半を待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:20.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로에게 놀림받은 무사시. 칼을 손에 넣을 수 있을 것인가? 질풍노도의 후반을 기다려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:20.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi was insulted by Kojirō. Will he ever get a sword? Wait for the stormy latter half!
Comment: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,捕まえただス！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잡았소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Caught one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おなかすいただス！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배고프오...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hungry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:53.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあ、ムサシさん。あたしが作ったお結びよ！たくさん食べて！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:53.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 무사시 씨. 제가 만든 주먹밥이에요. 많이 드세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:53.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here, Musashi. I made these rice balls for you. Eat as much as you want!
Comment: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ありがとう、オツルさん。いただくでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,고맙소, 오츠루 씨. 잘 먹겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you for all of these-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, Otsuru.
Comment: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.54,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オツルさん、これかたいでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨, 이거 딱딱하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru, these are tough-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,,かたいでござる。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,딱딱하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Tough...
Comment: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,オツルさん。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru...
Comment: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,食べられないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,먹을 수가 없소.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,I can't eat-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん！お兄ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,형! 형!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey there! Brother!
Comment: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん、なんで石なんかかじってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,형 왜 돌을 갉아?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Brother, why are you gnawing on stones?
Comment: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,腹が、腹が減って動けないんでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배, 배가 고파서 못 움직이겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,I... I am too hungry to move-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,じゃ、お兄ちゃん、これ上げるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 형! 이거 먹어!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here, brother! You can have this!
Comment: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、食った、食った！満腹でござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 잘 먹었소! 배가 부르오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was good! I am full-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:44.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,坊や、ありがとう。お兄ちゃん人心地がついたでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:44.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,얘야, 고맙소. 형 제정신을 되찾았소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:44.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, kid, that really saved me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でも、もしかしと、うちの人に持っていく魚だったんじゃないだスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도... 혹시 집으로 가져갈 물고기 아니었소?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,But... weren't you going to take that fishes to your home-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ！これでまたとるから！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,괜찮아! 이걸로 또 잡으면 되니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's all right! I can catch them again with this!
Comment: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よし！それじゃお兄ちゃんが取ってあげるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋아! 그럼 형이 잡아주오!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,All right! If that's the case, brother will catch for you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やったでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,해냈소!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,I did it!
Comment: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんすごい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,형 대단해!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're awesome!
Comment: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ありがとう！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,고마워!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんの、なんのでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아무것도 아니오.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was nothing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:17.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかしその籏は言い切れはずでござるだスな。だれが作ったんだスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:17.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도 그 작살은 좋은 잘 듣는 칼인데... 누가 만들었소?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:17.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,But still, that harpoon pierces pretty nicely... Who made it?
Comment: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これはお父ちゃんが作ったんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이건 아빠가 만들었어!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,My dad made this!
Comment: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아빠?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dad?
Comment: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ジパング一の刀鍛冶、剣持コテツっていうんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지팡구 제일의 칼 장인, 켄모치 코테츠라고 해!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,The number one sword craftsman of Jipangu, Kenmochi Kotetsu!
Comment: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.89,Default,ja,0,0,0,,僕はその子供のコタロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 그 자식 코타로!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am his son, Kotarō!
Comment: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ラッキーだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,럭키하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Lucky-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だめだ、だめだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안된다, 안 돼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nope, no way.
Comment: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなこと言わず、どうかお願いしますだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 말 하지 마시고 어떻게든 부탁드리오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't say that, and please help-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、どうしても名人の刀が欲しいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 어떻게든 명인의 칼을 원하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,I really want a sword from a master craftsman-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わしは刀鍛冶はやめたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 칼 장인은 관뒀다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,I gave up being one!
Comment: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:46.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そこ一つ、何とか、おいらをジパングナンバー1の武芸者にしてくださいだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:46.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,딱 하나만, 어떻게든, 절 지팡구 제일의 무예가가 되게 해 주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:46.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please, just one for me! Help me become the number one martial artist of Jipangu!
Comment: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:52.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だがジパングナンバー1になるのはお前の努力だ。わしがそうさせるわけではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:52.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 지팡구 제일이 되는 건 네 노력이다. 내가 그렇게 해주는 게 아니라!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:52.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,But it's your effort alone that will make you become the number one in Jipangu. I can't make you become one!
Comment: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:58.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,分かってるだス！おいら、これから一生懸命努力するだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:58.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알고 있소! 저, 지금부터 목숨을 걸고 노력하겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:58.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,I already know-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! From now on, I'll risk my life for that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でも。。。でも。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도... 그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,But... still...
Comment: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、どうしても名人の刀が欲しいんだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나... 어떻게든 명인의 칼을 원하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,I... really want a sword from a master craftsman-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お願いだス！名人の刀が欲しいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오! 명인의 칼을 갖고 싶소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I want a sword from an expert-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,欲しいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,원하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,I want one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,困った奴だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,곤란한 놈이군.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,What should I do with him?
Comment: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,刀が欲しいだスよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼 갖고 싶소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,I want a sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,,刀が。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sword...
Comment: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:30.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシは一度こうと決めたらしつこかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:30.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 한번 정하면 끈덕졌다.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:30.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Once decided, Musashi was persistent.
Comment: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:35.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お頼み申すだス！どうしても刀が欲しいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:35.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오! 어떻게든 칼을 원하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:35.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I want a sword no matter whatever it takes-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:39.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お頼み申しだス！名人の刀が欲しいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:39.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오! 명인의 칼이 갖고 싶소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:39.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I want a sword of an expert-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:43.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,-どうかこのムサシのお願いを聞いておくれだス。\N-父ちゃん。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:43.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-어떻게든 부탁드리오! 돈도 드리겠소!\N-아빠...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:43.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Please help me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'll pay you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!\N-Dad...
Comment: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:47.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お頼み申しだス。おいら、ジパングナンバー1の武芸者に。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:47.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오! 나, 지팡구 제일의 무예가로...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:47.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I need to be the number one martial artist of Jipangu...
Comment: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ボクデン師匠、悔しいだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보쿠덴 스승님... 분하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master Bokuden... I am so mortified-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ボクデン？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보쿠덴?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bokuden?
Comment: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、もうジパングナンバー1になれないだス。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 이제 지팡구 제일이 되지 못하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won't be able to become the number one anymore...
Comment: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これ！ムサシ！起きろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어이! 무사시! 일어나라!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! Musashi! Wake up!
Comment: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、あ、おはようございますだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아! 좋은 아침이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ah! Good morning-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,少々尋ねるが、お前の剣の師匠は誰だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,몇 가지 묻겠다만, 네 검의 스승은 누구냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,I must ask you; who is the master you learned swordsmanship from?
Comment: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらの師匠はツカハラボクデンだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,제 스승은 츠카하라 보쿠덴이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,My master is Tsukahara Bokuden-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,嘘をつくな！ボクデン殿は弟子は取らないはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거짓말하지 마라! 보쿠덴 님은 제자를 받지 않을 터이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not lie! Bokuden does not take students!
Comment: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:32.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,で、でもおいら、間違いなく弟子でござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:32.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 근데 나 틀림없이 제자이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:32.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bu- but I really am his student-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.52,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ならばボクデン殿の剣の究極の目標を行ってみろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다면 보쿠덴 님의 검의 궁극의 목적을 말해 보아라!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then tell me, the ultimate purpose of a sword, according to Master Bokuden!
Comment: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えっと、なんだっけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어... 뭐였더라?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Uh... what was it?
Comment: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,-どうした。\N-えっと。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-왜 그러나?\N-저...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,-What's the problem?\N-Um...
Comment: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やはり偽物だな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 가짜구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,You were lying at all!
Comment: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいら、嘘はつかないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 거짓말은 하지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,I do not lie-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.00,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ならば申してみろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 대 보아라!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then tell me right now!
Comment: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だめだな、こりゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안 되겠어, 이 녀석.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is going nowhere.
Comment: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:59.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ！ちょっと！思い出しただス！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:59.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아! 잠깐! 기억났소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:59.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait! Just a moment! I remembered!
Comment: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:13.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,剣の究極は戦わずして勝つことなり、武道の武の字はそもそも矛と<みととくほこ>すなわち、武器を止めることなり、老子はよく敵に勝つものは争わず。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:10.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,검의 궁극은 싸우지 않고 이기는 것. 무도의 무(武) 자는 원래 창(戈)을 막는다(止)는 의미, 즉, 무기를 멈추는 것.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,노자(老子)는 적을 잘 이기는 자는 싸우지 않는다고 했소.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,The true meaning of a sword is to win without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:10.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Solidness(武) of martial arts(武道) originally means to stop(止) a spear(戈); in other words, to stop a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,To borrow the words of Laozi, the one who easily defeats an enemy does not engage.
Comment: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,見事じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good job!
Comment: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい！ありがとうでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예! 감사하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そもそもわしが刀鍛冶をやめたのにはわけがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,애초에 내가 칼 장인를 관둔 것에는 이유가 있다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,I have a reason why I stopped being a sword craftsman.
Comment: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,まず、いかなる剣にも魂が宿っておることを知れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,먼저 어떠한 검에도 혼이 깃들어 있음을 알고,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,First, you must know that a sword has a spirit.
Comment: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:31.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,剣にはそれを作ったもの、使うものの思いがこもる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:31.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,검에는 그것을 만든 자와 쓰는 자의 생각이 담겨 있다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:31.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,A sword inherits the mind of the crafter and the yielder.
Comment: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その心が邪なものならば、剣はじゃけんとなり、
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 마음이 부정한 자라면 검은 사견이 되어,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,To one with a wicked mind, the sword would also become so,
Comment: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:38.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ただの命をあやめる道具にすぎ。分かるか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:38.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,단지 생명을 빼앗는 도구에 불과하다. 알겠나?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:38.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,ending up as nothing more than a tool to take lives away. Do you understand?
Comment: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:44.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よくわからないだスが、おいら、人を殺すために刀は使わないだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:44.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘은 모르겠지만 나는 사람을 죽이기 위해 칼을 쓰지 않소.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:44.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't really understand-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, but I don't use swords to kill people-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:48.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よく言った、ムサシ。お前の目は本当によく住んでおるぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:48.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 말했다, 무사시. 네 눈이 참 맑구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:48.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Well said, Musashi. Your eyes are clear.
Comment: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,よく寝た後だから。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 자고 난 후니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Because I had a good sleep.
Comment: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ、よく聞け！わしはお前のためにもう一度だけ刀を作る。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시. 잘 들어라. 나는 널 위해 다시 한번만 칼을 만들겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, listen well. I will make swords for you for the last time.
Comment: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ほ、本当だスか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저, 정말이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Re- really?!
Comment: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:02.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ただし、お前も一緒に剣を作るものの心を学ぶがよい。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:02.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나, 너도 함께 검을 만드는 자의 마음을 배우는 것이 좋다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:02.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,But you will have to learn the mind of sword craftsman.
Comment: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:02.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:02.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:02.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right!
Comment: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:13.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,日本刀の材料は、地面の中で長い眠りについていた純度の高い砂鉄である。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:13.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,일본도의 재료는 땅 안에 오랫동안 잠자고 있던 순도가 높은 사철이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:13.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,The material of Japanese swords is iron sand of high purity that slept for a long time under the grond.
Comment: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:19.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,この砂鉄を何千回、何万回も心をこめて鍛えて作り上げるのである。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:19.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 사철을 몇천 회, 몇만 회 마음을 담아 단련시켜 만드는 것이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:19.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,The iron sand must be forged thousands and millions of times wholeheartedly in order to make one.
Comment: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,{???}まだですらいのかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아직 안 된 걸까나...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're still not done yet...
Comment: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,-うわ、できた！\N-おお、できた！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-해냈다!\N-해냈구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,-We did it!\N-We did it!
Comment: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.61,Default,ja,0,0,0,,{???}-おっと、やっただス！うわ、やった、やった！万歳だス！\N-ちょっとおってしたぞ！ははは、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-해냈소! 만세이오!\N-참 잘 했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,-We did it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Hooray-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!\N-Good job!
Comment: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:49.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ、これがわしがこの世で作った最後の剣。心して使え。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:49.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시, 이것이 내가 이 세상에서 만든 마지막 검일 테다. 마음을 담아 써라.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:49.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, these will be the last swords that I make in this world. Use them to the fullest.
Comment: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ありがとうでございますだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말 감사하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you so much-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:03.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コテツ殿！あれ、おいらも急に眠くなって。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:03.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코테츠 님! 어라? 나도 갑자기 피곤해졌...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:03.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master Kotetsu! Huh? I suddenly got sleepy...
Comment: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:15.92,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あなた！大変です！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:15.92,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여보! 큰일입니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:15.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dear! Big problem!
Comment: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ど、どうしたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무, 무슨 일인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wha- what's going on?
Comment: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ヨシオカ道場の人たちが来て。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,요시오카 도장의 사람들이 와서...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,People from Yoshioka Dōjō came and...
Comment: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なに？俺が頼んだ刀など作れないだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐라? 내가 부탁한 칼을 만들지 않겠다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,What? He didn't made the sword I asked?
Comment: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どなた様のご依頼でもOKすることは出来かねます！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떤 분의 의뢰라도 들을 수 없습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,We will not accept any request from anyone!
Comment: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ならばどうなっても作らせてみせるぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다면 어떻게든 만들게 하겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then I'll make him make one!
Comment: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,-おい！\N-は！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-어이!\N-예!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,-You know what to do!\N-Yes!
Comment: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何をなさるんですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭘 하시는 것입니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Comment: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:43.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,助けて！怖いよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:43.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살려줘! 무서워!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:43.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Help! I'm scared!
Comment: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:48.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,倅はコテツの剣と交換だ。おやじにそう伝えろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:48.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네 아이는 코테츠의 검과 교환하겠다. 그렇게 전해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:48.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will exchange your child for a sword made by Kotetsu. Tell him so!
Comment: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,助けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살려줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Help me!
Comment: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コタロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코타로!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kotarō!
Comment: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:06.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんという卑劣な連中だ。コタローはこのおいらの命に代えても助けるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:06.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 무슨 비열한 패거리오. 코타로는 이 목숨과 교환해서라도 구해내겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:06.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a cowardly gang. I will save Kotarō even if I have to exchange my life for him-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コタロー！待つんだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코타로! 기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kotarō! I'm going to save you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
