Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:17.61,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs64\frz-89.7\frx2\fax0.1\move(558,372,558,372)}Yoshioka Dōjō Inc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:17.61,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs36\frz-89.7\frx2\fax0.1\move(512,168,512,168)}Sakai Branch
Comment: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシが来ただが！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시가 왔다!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi has appeared!
Comment: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,-ムサシが！\N-逃げねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-무사시가!\N-네이놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Musashi!\N-How dare you!
Comment: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ見参でござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 등장이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,心配はいらん！峰打ちでござるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,걱정할 필요는 없소! 칼등이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,No need to worry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! It was the back side-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ、覚悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시, 각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだ、あの構えは。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐냐, 저 자세는!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is that posture?
Comment: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ！これが目に入らぬか！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 이게 눈에 들어오지 않는가!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Don't you see this?!
Comment: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コ、コタロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코, 코타로!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ko- Kotarō!
Comment: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,無駄な抵抗はやめよう。さもないとこの子の命はないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쓸데없는 저항은 관둬라! 그렇지 않으면 이 얘의 목숨은 없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Give up with your futile resistance! Or this kid dies!
Comment: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ！刀を捨てろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 칼을 내려둬라!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Put down your sword!
Comment: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お、お父ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아빠!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,D- dad!
Comment: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コタロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코타로!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kotarō!
Comment: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,許せん、デンシチロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,용서할 수 없소, 덴시치로!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unforgivable, Densichirō!
Comment: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:30.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,た、助けてくれ。か、金ならいくらでも出す。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:30.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사, 살려줘. 돈이라면 얼마라도 줄 테니!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:30.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Spare me. I'll give you money as much as you want!
Comment: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,許せん！お前は地獄に落ちるだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,용서할 수 없소! 넌 지옥으로 보내주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unforgivable-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I will send you to hell-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシ！やめんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 관두지 못할까!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Stop that right now!
Comment: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,止めてくれるなだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈추지 마시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't stop me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もう忘れたか、ムサシ！剣は人あやめるためにあるのではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,벌써 잊었냐, 무사시! 검은 위해를 가하기 위해 쓰이는 것이 아니라고!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Did you forget already, Musashi?! A sword does not exist to injure a person!
Comment: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ボクデン殿もそういわれたはずだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보쿠덴 님도 그렇게 말했을 테다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master Bokuden would said so too!
Comment: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こんな奴をあやめたら刀が汚れるだけじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 놈을 죽이면 검이 더럽혀질 뿐이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you kill this guy, you just end up disgracing your sword!
Comment: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,わ、分かったでござるだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 알겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Alright-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:18.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こうしてムサシは名刀コタツを手に入れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:17.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이렇게 무사시는 명도 코테츠를 손에 넣었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:17.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,And this is how Musashi has managed to get the excellent swords, Kotetsu.
Comment: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:23.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そしてまたこの日、はの有名な二刀流が誕生したのであるが、
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:23.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그리고 또 그 날, 그 유명한 이도류가 탄생한 것이었지만,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:23.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,And also, on that day, that famous dual blade has born,
Comment: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:27.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ムサシはまだ気づいてはいなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:27.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 아직 깨닫지 못하였다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:27.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,but Musashi is yet to realize.
