Comment: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,師匠。言い響きだスな。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승, 좋은 울림을 가진 단어이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master. A word with good echo-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:10.87,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ついにおいらも弟子を持つようになっただス。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:10.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,결국엔 나도 제자를 가지게 되었소!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:10.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Finally, I got a student-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:17.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,弟子っていうものは便利出すな。お金の心配しないで団子は食べられるし、道案内もしてくれるし。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:17.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,제자라는 것은 편리하오! 돈 걱정 없이 단고를 먹게 해 주고, 길을 안내해 주고.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:17.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,A student is convinient! He lets me eat dangos without worry, and guides my path.
Comment: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:20.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でも、この弟子って、おいらより強いんだスね。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:20.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,근데 이 제자라는 자, 나보다 강하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:20.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,But this student is powerful than me, heh...
Comment: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:24.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,次回！おいらは師匠だ！エライだス。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:24.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다음 이야기! 나는 스승이오. 훌륭하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:24.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next story! I am a Master! Excellent!
Comment: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:27.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,疾風怒濤の活躍を見るだス！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:27.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,질풍노도의 활약을 보시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:27.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Be sure to check out the next stormy story-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.03,0:24:30.99,NoteOnAnime,ko,60,0,60,,{\an7}다음 이야기
Comment: 0,0:24:27.03,0:24:30.99,TitleEP,ja,0,0,70,,おいらは師匠だ！エライだス
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.03,0:24:30.99,TitleEP,ko,0,0,70,,나는 스승이오\N훌륭하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.03,0:24:30.99,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}기대하세요!
